data.description: Buyers Loss is your Gain! Charming and cozy is what describes this updated rowhome nestled in the desirable Clearing neighborhood very close to Midway Airport. This home was rehabbed in 2013 featuring 2 bedrooms 2 full ceramic baths d boasting hardwood flooring throughout, decorative wainscoting detail in the living room and dining room areas, complemented with tray ceilings and can lighting. The galley style kitchen features cherry cabinetry, marble/stone backsplash, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances: sliding patio door open onto spacious wooden pergola deck with multiple seating perfect for outdoor entertaining. The home has a finished basement with walk-out access to the yard and an oversized driveway accommodating 2-3 parking spaces  Excellent location next door to the park, easy access to public transportation and expressways. A MUST SEE!
